---
---

<section class="testimonials section" id="resultados">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="testimonials__header reveal">
      <p class="eyebrow">Resultados</p>
      <h2 class="display-lg">
        <span>Clientes que</span><br/>
        <span class="gradient-text">confían en nosotros.</span>
      </h2>
    </div>

    <div class="testimonials__grid">
      <div class="testimonial reveal">
        <div class="testimonial__result">
          <span class="testimonial__number">+50%</span>
          <span class="testimonial__label">ventas en promedio</span>
        </div>
        <p class="testimonial__text">"Transformaron notre negocio. Duplicamos ventas en 3 meses."</p>
        <span class="testimonial__author">—  Tienda Online</span>
      </div>

      <div class="testimonial reveal reveal-delay-1">
        <div class="testimonial__result">
          <span class="testimonial__number">24/7</span>
          <span class="testimonial__label">atención automática</span>
        </div>
        <p class="testimonial__text">"Nuestro chatbot atiende siempre. Sin perder clientes."</p>
        <span class="testimonial__author">— Gerente</span>
      </div>

      <div class="testimonial reveal reveal-delay-2">
        <div class="testimonial__result">
          <span class="testimonial__number">-70%</span>
          <span class="testimonial__label">tiempo en tareas</span>
        </div>
        <p class="testimonial__text">"Sistema automatizado. Nos permite enfocarnos en crecer."</p>
        <span class="testimonial__author">— Director, Empresa de servicios</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .testimonials {
    background: var(--bg-base);
    padding: var(--section-py) 0;
  }

  .testimonials__header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3rem);
  }

  .testimonials__header h2 span:first-child {
    display: block;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .testimonials__header h2 span:first-child {
      display: inline;
    }
  }

  /* Grid */
  .testimonials__grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    max-width: 800px;
    margin-inline: auto;
  }

  @media (min-width: 640px) {
    .testimonials__grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    }
  }

  /* Testimonial */
  .testimonial {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    background: var(--bg-surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);
    border-radius: 1rem;
  }

  .testimonial__result {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .testimonial__number {
    display: block;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--accent);
  }

  .testimonial__label {
    display: block;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }

  .testimonial__text {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    font-weight: 500;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    line-height: 1.4;
  }

  .testimonial__author {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-style: italic;
  }
</style>
